{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_02_03",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 02 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、応援ありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all for your support!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.264603233337402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "TRINITYAiLE、でしたー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This was TRINITYAiLE~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.464603233337402,
      "endTime": 7.295102167129516,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.333333333333,
          "startTime": 6.597936566670735
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――TRINITYAiLEは、その圧倒的な実力で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――With their overwhelming talent‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.497936566670735,
      "endTime": 10.857936509450276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "瞬く間に若手トップに躍り出ていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE quickly rose to the top of the young idol scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.857936509450235,
      "endTime": 13.097936471303266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 13.897936471303336
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 13.897936566670735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、優ちゃん、お疲れさま！\n今日も最っ高のステージになったね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ Yu-chan‚ good work!\nIt was another fantastic stage today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.531269900004068,
      "endTime": 21.172426382700603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ～……いつも以上にお客さんも熱くて\nめっちゃ盛り上がったわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah~… The audience was even more passionate than usual‚\nand we really got them fired up~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.368514808019004,
      "endTime": 27.58835609753927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 21.368514808019036
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 27.78785103451122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、手応えのあるステージだったわね\nでも……まだまだ、満足はしないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ it was a rewarding stage.\nBut… I’m not satisfied yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.78785103451122,
      "endTime": 34.0593929160725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！\n次はもっともっと盛り上げていこうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nLet’s make it even more exciting next time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.27441247858182,
      "endTime": 37.93747366823331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 34.27441247858185
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 38.13980824634281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ……すみれちゃんも、瑠依ちゃんの\nストイックさが移ったみたい……あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu… Looks like you’ve picked up Rui-chan’s\nstoicism… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.13980824634284,
      "endTime": 44.69783532306403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 44.88425385123426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "あそこにおるん、朝倉さんやな\nそれと、隣にいるのは……LizNoirの二人？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that President Asakura over there?\nAnd the two people next to him… Are they from LizNoir?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.88425385123426,
      "endTime": 52.78425375586683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 52.97524478294279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir。バンプロ所属の人気グループで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――LizNoir‚ a popular group belonging to Bump Production‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.97524478294279,
      "endTime": 56.335244848337595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEよりも先輩にあたるアイドルだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "are senior idols to TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.34191144960949,
      "endTime": 59.84191151772909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 60.04191144960949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長い活動休止を経て復帰して以来",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Since returning from a long hiatus‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.04191144960949,
      "endTime": 62.421911552420234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 62.408578116276125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "数ヶ月で数々の記録を塗り替え続けている強者である",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they’ve been rewriting numerous records in just a few months.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.408578116276125,
      "endTime": 65.7685782614207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 65.97524478294278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "本当ね……何話してるのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right… I wonder what they’re talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.97524478294278,
      "endTime": 69.37424714424039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 69.57424714424039
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "なんや瑠依ちゃん、気になるん？\nむしろ、朝倉さんに構ってもらえなくて寂しいとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with ya‚ Rui-chan? You interested?\nOr are ya lonely that President Asakura’s not paying attention to ya?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.57424714424039,
      "endTime": 76.42175299980069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 76.64091381090702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "もう、違うわよ\n私が気になってるのはLizNoirの方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ no!\nI’m interested in LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.64091381090705,
      "endTime": 81.73445142763678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 81.94091381090703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風に社長と話してる所\n初めて見たから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve never seen them\ntalking to the president like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.94091381090706,
      "endTime": 85.74091381090706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 85.93939865939186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所なのに、ほとんど喋ったことないもんね\nいろいろお話してみたいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we’re in the same agency‚ we’ve hardly ever talked to them.\nI want to talk to them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.93939865939191,
      "endTime": 92.6563145529466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 92.87273199272522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、LizNoir、こっち来るなぁ\n出番みたいやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ LizNoir’s coming over here.\nLooks like it’s their turn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.87273199272522,
      "endTime": 97.67273199272522,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 60.60134060811606,
          "startTime": 92.93333333333334
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.666666666614,
          "startTime": 98.03939865939184
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 99.3060653260585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれ？　無視されちゃった？\n……むー！　なんか悔しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Did they just ignore us?\n…Ugh! It’s kinda frustrating!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3060653260585,
      "endTime": 106.53765254529678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 106.7393986593919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……芸歴はともかく、実力は負けていないはず\nなのに、どうしてこんなに距離を感じるんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Regardless of experience‚ our abilities shouldn’t be inferior.\nBut why do I feel such a distance…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7393986593919,
      "endTime": 114.86905859820415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "目を向けている場所が違うからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because you’re looking at the wrong place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0748893531648,
      "endTime": 117.52488944853224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 117.72488944853224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "しゃ、社長……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-President…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.72488944853224,
      "endTime": 119.68142006719984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 119.88142006719984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央は、同世代のアイドルになど興味はないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio isn’t interested in idols of her generation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.88142006719984,
      "endTime": 123.96159163452562,
